channel.title: I cant login mosparscape! please help!
channel.description:
I cant login in mosparscape! please help! I open Moparscape and while its loading all this comes up
"News: For online servers, look at the News: server status list at moparisthebest.com News: News: -moparisthebest Server : 127.0.0.1
Loaded 0 random handlers # Loading controllers "
When the loading bar finishes this comes up -> "Load error: ondemand"
And when I login any server I put the Port and Server number i want to go in and press connect... But the problem is it freezes on -> "Connecting to Server" And When my brother is playing on another computer in the same server i am trying to log in... when i try and connect it appears on is game "andrecook(my nick) logged in" but on my pc it dosent go further then "connecting to server"
Can someone please help me! Thnks
